ActEmergency Management Act
SubjectProvincial Emergency Financial Assistance Order No. 263, Northwest Territories
PrecisPROVINCIAL EMERGENCY FINANCIAL ASSISTANCE ORDER No. 263 in order to (1) declare the natural disaster to be of concern to the federal government; and (2) authorize the provision of financial assistance to Northwest Territories with respect to the interface fires that occurred from May 14 to September 22, 2023.
